CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 7, 1956, pg. A14 reads: "Designs Transformers - Donald Scott designs transformers for the Canonsburg Transformer Company, which sends its products throughout the world. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Donald Scott reading "Electrical Engineering" magazine, seated in a chair in interior with light colored walls and a small table on right with telephone
